{
  "stem": "18068.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 204.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had one girl there, she was about 16, and she was a very good-- a German girl-- very good worker, very conscientious.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when she saw these men, she told us she belonged to the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said you couldn't help herself, because they enjoy themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the girls and boys, it was good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what she did, she tore her card up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because you could speak Yiddish--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only like, hardly a village, just a few houses there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was brought home to us in actual facts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Up to now it was just theory-- hearsay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But now we saw it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt sad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Thinking that my people came from Lithuania, and if they didn't get married, they would have been there, yes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to think about it a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it's only thoughts, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was brought home to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They all disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the unit that I was with was an invasion unit, trained for invasion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the war in Japan was still on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in Europe it was finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- the government decided to bring our unit back to England, to fit us out with new clothes for-- for jungle warfare.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were going for the invasion of the Japanese landings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A town, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there, and we were going to be brought back to England to be fitted out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then the bomb dropped in Japan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they brought us back to Germany again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was saved for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were only in villages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A place called [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mettigan, ?] I think.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
